message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which has been meticulously designed and crafted to exceed your expectations. This exceptional item is valued at $12000 by us, reflecting its quality, functionality, and exclusivity. We believe it holds significant value for you as well, given your needs and preferences. Please consider this offer carefully and let us know if you have any questions or require further information. We look forward to the possibility of serving you with our top-tier product.
